{"title":"Gallery","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Gallery","subtitle":"光影之间 · Moments in Light","filters":["lightbox"],"lightbox":{"match":"auto","effect":"fade","loop":true},"toc":false,"page-layout":"full"},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<style>\n/* ========== 全局背景 ========== */\n.quarto-container {\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, \n    var(--bs-body-bg) 0%, \n    color-mix(in srgb, var(--bs-body-bg) 95%, var(--bs-primary)) 100%\n  );\n}\n\n/* ========== 优雅分隔线 ========== */\n.elegant-divider {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  margin: 3rem 0 2.5rem;\n  gap: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.elegant-divider::before,\n.elegant-divider::after {\n  content: '';\n  flex: 1;\n  max-width: 200px;\n  height: 1px;\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, \n    transparent, \n    var(--bs-secondary), \n    transparent\n  );\n}\n\n.divider-symbol {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  color: var(--bs-secondary);\n  letter-spacing: 8px;\n}\n\n/* ========== 章节标题 ========== */\n.section-title {\n  font-family: \"Cormorant Garamond\", Georgia, serif;\n  font-size: 2rem;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;\n  color: var(--bs-heading-color);\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.section-title::after {\n  content: '';\n  display: block;\n  width: 60px;\n  height: 2px;\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, \n    transparent, \n    var(--bs-primary), \n    transparent\n  );\n  margin: 0.8rem auto 0;\n}\n\n/* ========== 介绍文字 ========== */\n.intro-text {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-family: \"Cormorant Garamond\", Georgia, serif;\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  font-style: italic;\n  color: var(--bs-secondary-color);\n  max-width: 650px;\n  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;\n  line-height: 1.9;\n  letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n}\n\n/* ========== 画廊容器 ========== */\n.gallery-wrapper {\n  background: var(--bs-tertiary-bg);\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  padding: 2rem;\n  margin: 1.5rem 0;\n  box-shadow: \n    0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),\n    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n}\n\n/* ========== 图片样式 ========== */\n.quarto-figure {\n  margin: 0.75rem;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.quarto-figure img {\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n  filter: brightness(0.95) saturate(1.05);\n}\n\n.quarto-figure img:hover {\n  transform: scale(1.03);\n  filter: brightness(1) saturate(1.1);\n  box-shadow: \n    0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.2),\n    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n}\n\n/* ========== 隐藏默认标题 ========== */\nfigcaption {\n  display: none; \n}\n\n/* ========== 提示框 ========== */\n.gallery-tip {\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 1.5rem;\n  margin-top: 3rem;\n  font-family: \"Cormorant Garamond\", Georgia, serif;\n  font-style: italic;\n  color: var(--bs-secondary-color);\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, \n    var(--bs-tertiary-bg) 0%, \n    transparent 100%\n  );\n}\n\n/* ========== 页脚装饰 ========== */\n.footer-ornament {\n  text-align: center;\n  margin: 3rem 0 1rem;\n  font-size: 1.8rem;\n  letter-spacing: 12px;\n  color: var(--bs-secondary);\n  opacity: 0.5;\n}\n\n/* ========== 响应式 ========== */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .gallery-wrapper {\n    padding: 1rem;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n  }\n  \n  .intro-text {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    padding: 0 1rem;\n  }\n  \n  .section-title {\n    font-size: 1.6rem;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n\n<!-- Google Fonts -->\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n::: {.intro-text}\nA curated collection of moments — from sweeping landscapes to intimate urban scenes.  \nEach photograph tells its own quiet story.\n:::\n\n<div class=\"elegant-divider\"><span class=\"divider-symbol\">✦</span></div>\n\n::: {.section-title}\nLandscapes & Cityscapes\n:::\n\n::: {.gallery-wrapper}\n::: {layout-ncol=2}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-01.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-04.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-05.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-06.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-07.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-02.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n:::\n:::\n\n<div class=\"elegant-divider\"><span class=\"divider-symbol\">✦</span></div>\n\n::: {.section-title}\nVertical Perspectives\n:::\n\n::: {.gallery-wrapper}\n::: {layout-ncol=3}\n\n![](images/gallery/gallery-03.jpeg){group=\"main-gallery\"}\n\n:::\n:::\n\n<div class=\"elegant-divider\"><span class=\"divider-symbol\">· · ·</span></div>\n\n::: {.gallery-tip}\n✨ Click on any image to view in full screen\n:::\n\n::: {.footer-ornament}\n◆\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<style>\n/* ========== 全局背景 ========== */\n.quarto-container {\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, \n    var(--bs-body-bg) 0%, \n    color-mix(in srgb, var(--bs-body-bg) 95%, var(--bs-primary)) 100%\n  );\n}\n\n/* ========== 优雅分隔线 ========== */\n.elegant-divider {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  margin: 3rem 0 2.5rem;\n  gap: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.elegant-divider::before,\n.elegant-divider::after {\n  content: '';\n  flex: 1;\n  max-width: 200px;\n  height: 1px;\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, \n    transparent, \n    var(--bs-secondary), \n    transparent\n  );\n}\n\n.divider-symbol {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  color: var(--bs-secondary);\n  letter-spacing: 8px;\n}\n\n/* ========== 章节标题 ========== */\n.section-title {\n  font-family: \"Cormorant Garamond\", Georgia, serif;\n  font-size: 2rem;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;\n  color: var(--bs-heading-color);\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.section-title::after {\n  content: '';\n  display: block;\n  width: 60px;\n  height: 2px;\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, \n    transparent, \n    var(--bs-primary), \n    transparent\n  );\n  margin: 0.8rem a